data.description: UNBEATABLE VALUE FOR THE HOLIDAYS!  PRICE RECENTLY REDUCED TO $320,000.  BUT THAT'S NOT ALL!!  TO MAKE THIS HOLIDAY SEASON TRULY SPECIAL, THIS GENEROUS SELLER IS OFFERING $10,000 IN BUYER CONCESSIONS!!  SAVE BIG!!  PREMIUM PROPERTY = AFFORDABLE PRICE!!  This beautiful and modern ground floor condo offers a perfect combination of comfort and convenience. With 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this turn-key property is a comfortable place to call home but also vacation rental approved, making it an excellent investment opportunity. Perfect location - just a 3-minute walk to the beach, and only 5 minutes away from the lively entertainment district, Gravity Park, and the charming Sand Castle Village. All-new kitchen appliances, makes meal preparation a breeze. The spacious living room is elegantly furnished, creating a welcoming atmosphere for relaxation after a day of exploring the beach and local attractions. Refrigerator-2021, Dishwasher/Stove-2023, Gel Sleeper Sofa-2023, A/C condenser 2022.
